Ready state maps to OCI ACTIVE.
Requeue continues while OCI reports CREATING
during create or DELETING during delete
confirmation.
Bind-before-create reuses only exact
compartment, availability-domain,
Lustre-file-system, and display-name matches
that remain in ACTIVE or CREATING.
Create and update settle from the
ObjectStorageLink read model; delete is the only
work-request-backed phase.
Delete completes after GetObjectStorageLink or
ListObjectStorageLinks returns DELETED or no
longer finds the resource.
